        <h3>ConnexOntario</h3>
        <p>Free referral service to mental health and addiction care across Ontario. Call <strong>1-866-531-2600</strong> or visit <strong>connexontario.ca</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card">
        <h3>Your Family Doctor / Primary Care</h3>
        <p>A good starting point for referrals to addiction medicine, psychiatry, or counselling — especially if medication-assisted treatment is something you're considering or already using.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-card">
        <h3>Ontario Health atHome</h3>
        <p>Navigating the care system in Ontario: <strong>ontariohealthathome.ca</strong> connects you to local services including mental health support.</p>
      </div>
